## add a folder with same name as package (add __init__.py)
```
my_cpp_pkg/
├── CMakeLists.txt
├── package.xml
├── include/
├── src/
└── **my_cpp_pkg/** <-- This folder's name must match the package name
    ├── **__init__.py** <-- Must be here to be a package
    └── **my_utility.py** <-- can be imported by other packages
```

## CmakeList.txt
```
find_package(ament_cmake_python REQUIRED)
find_package(rclpy REQUIRED)

ament_python_install_package(${PROJECT_NAME})
```

## package.xml
```
<buildtool_depend>ament_cmake_python</buildtool_depend>
```
